  "title": "Unexpected datetime type change after changing MAX to AVG",
  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\n```\nDROP DATABASE IF EXISTS test;\nCREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS test;\nUSE test;\nCREATE TABLE t2 (c13 DATETIME NULL);\nINSERT t2 (c13) VALUES ('2025-03-23 19:05:28');\nSELECT AVG(c13) , MAX(c13) FROM t2;\n```\n\n<!-- a step by step guide for reproducing the bug. -->\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\n\ncol_1's type  should be DATETIME instead of DOUBLE\n\n```\nmysql> SELECT AVG(c13) , MAX(c13) FROM t2;\n+---------------------+---------------------+\n| AVG(c13)            | MAX(c13)            |\n+---------------------+---------------------+\n| 20250323190528.0000 | 2025-03-23 19:05:28 |\n+---------------------+---------------------+\n1 row in set (0.00 sec)\n\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\n\nmysql> SELECT AVG(c13) , MAX(c13) FROM t2;\n+---------------------+---------------------+\n| AVG(c13)            | MAX(c13)            |\n+---------------------+---------------------+\n| 20250323190528.0000 | 2025-03-23 19:05:28 |\n+---------------------+---------------------+\n1 row in set (0.00 sec)\n```\n### 4. What is your TiDB version? (Required)\n\n<!-- Paste the output of SELECT tidb_version() -->\n```\nmysql> select tidb_version();\n+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| tidb_version()                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |\n+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------